</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/27156.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27156/indexMediumPc2/27156.jpg?1463800254" alt="巴菲特出手之后，各类投资人会如何评估苹果公司的股票？">
		
		<p class="category">
